quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  107,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  107,1,tum ne dekha uss shakhs ko jo akhirat ki jaza o saza ko jhutlata hai ?
  107,2,wohi to hai jo yateem ko dhakkay deta hai
  107,3,aur maskeen ko khana dainay par nahi aksata
  107,4,phir tabahi hai unn namaz parhnay walon ke liye
  107,5,jo apni namaz se ghaflat brtte hain
  107,6,jo riya kaari karte hain
  107,7,aur mamooli zaroorat ki cheeze ( logon ko ) dainay se guraiz karte hain
